title: Ram Balram
subTitle: Unaware of his evil intentions and his role in killing their parents, two brothers Ram and Balram fall victim to their deceitful uncle. They must unite to foil his plans of gaining wealth.

title: Teri Kasam
subTitle: Dolly, a rich and spoilt woman, falls for Tony, a poor musician, and marries him. However, her arrogance begins to create problems in their marital life.

title: Maharaja
subTitle: Bored by his monotonous lifestyle, Mahadevan, a middle-aged family man, longs to lead a modern life. However, everything begins to fall apart when he chooses to change his way of living.

title: International Crook
subTitle: Rajesh, the superintendent of the police, is happy to meet his old friend, Shekar, in Goa, unaware that he is a smuggler, who is involved in a spree of illegal activities.

title: Sikandar Sadak Ka
subTitle: When Sikander, a union worker, tries to stop his employer's misdeeds, the authorities jail him. After his release, Sikander is determined to seek revenge.

title: Daraar
subTitle: Raj Malhotra, a wealthy man, falls for Priya. However, things get complicated when Vikram, Priya's abusive husband, enters the frame.

title: Kismat
subTitle: Tony, a hitman, unwittingly puts the father of the girl he loves in deep trouble. He realises his blunder and sets out to put things straight, but it might be too late.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan
subTitle: Ram, an honest man, falls in love with a woman named Bijli and goes on to help the people of her village. However, the region's corrupt leader, Thakur Vijay Singh, soon begins to plot against him.

title: Mera Badla: Revenge
subTitle: Shankar Rao, a businessman, and his family start witnessing strange events in their house. Thereafter, he calls Dr Vijay, a psychiatrist, to help him.

title: Mera Badla: Revenge
subTitle: Shankar Rao, a businessman, and his family start witnessing strange events in their house. Thereafter, he calls Dr Vijay, a psychiatrist, to help him.

title: Jaane Jigar
subTitle: Two identical women who hail from different backgrounds fall in love with two best friends, Ravi and Vijay. Misunderstandings arise when Ravi and Vijay believe they are in love with the same girl.

title: Mukt
subTitle: Suyambulingam, a school drop-out but an intelligent man, acquires knowledge by watching movies. When a dark incident seems to ruin his family, he uses all his wits to protect them.

title: Karishma Kudrat Ka
subTitle: Vijay lives in a village with his family. He makes an enemy with Lala and a bandit, Bhagad, who devises a plan to throw the former out of the village.

title: Maati Maangey Khoon
subTitle: Hariya is clueless about his parents and discovers that his family was destroyed by Thakur Balram Singh. He vows to take revenge, especially after his friend, who is Balram's nephew, also opposes him.

title: Shehzaade
subTitle: Suraj, a justice-loving man, must face a series of obstacles when he discovers his widowed mother's affair with a former prisoner.

title: Wafadaar
subTitle: Chanda's parents disapprove of her boyfriend Ranga and want her to marry Prasad. Ranga is accused of having an affair with Sita.

title: Phool Aur Kaante
subTitle: Love leads Ajay down a new path when he is expected to inherit his father's criminal empire, bringing along perils that could either tear their family apart or solidify their bond.

title: Hindustani Yoddha
subTitle: A young orphan girl suffers at the hands of an evil woman who envies her melodious voice. When she loses hope, her music teacher narrates the story of a heroic man to inspire her.

title: Hindustani Yoddha
subTitle: A young orphan girl suffers at the hands of an evil woman who envies her melodious voice. When she loses hope, her music teacher narrates the story of a heroic man to inspire her.

title: Yes Boss
subTitle: Rahul's boss, Siddharth, is a womaniser who exploits Rahul into helping him win over Seema. However, Rahul ends up falling for Seema and is torn between his career aspirations and her.

title: Humjoli
subTitle: A misunderstanding leads to two college friends, Madhu and Sidhu turning bitter towards each other. However, circumstances reunite them for a friend.

title: Hatya: The Murder
subTitle: Ravi's father, Ratan, gets killed when he refuses to sell his land to Murugan, a wealthy businessman. Later, Ravi sets out to avenge the death of his father.

title: Mr. Natwarlal
subTitle: When Natwar's elder brother is framed for bribery, he decides to avenge his brother's humiliation and thus poses as a crime lord.

title: Chori Mera Kaam
subTitle: Chori Mera Kaam

title: Khiladi
subTitle: A group of four friends decide to play a prank involving the fake kidnapping of one of them and asking for ransom from her father. However, things become complicated when she actually ends up dead.

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Devta
subTitle: An ordinary taxi driver becomes part of a notorious gang through a twist of fate and takes on the role of a terrifying assassin.
